intro: Let the shopping fever get the best of you!
description:
Enter the world of shopping. Don't miss out on the best deals. Your appearance depends on how well you shop!  

The road to the top of the fashion heap isn't easy. Many obstacles await you. But don't be afraid and keep going! Avoid obstacles, collect shopping bags and diamonds to change your outfit and impress your friends. 

Reach the finish line with your hands full of amazing things. Try to collect as many branded goods as possible. Shock everyone around you with your bright and expensive look.  

Check out the new fun game from the NOSTRA.GAMES team. 

Hurry up to get the best deals!
